    .. math::

        \\begin{split}
           \hat{w} &= g\\frac{w}{\Vert w\Vert}\\\\
        \end{split}
 
        
    Reference : `Salimans, Kingma 2016 <https://arxiv.org/abs/1602.07868>`_
        
